Monthly averages

climate_data$Month = format(as.Date(climate_data$NewDate), format = "%m") 
climate_data$Year = format(climate_data$NewDate, format="%Y")

MonthlyTMAXMean = aggregate(TMAX ~ Month + Year, climate_data, mean)
MonthlyTMAXMean$YEAR = as.numeric(MonthlyTMAXMean$Year) 
MonthlyTMAXMean$MONTH = as.numeric(MonthlyTMAXMean$Month) 
str(MonthlyTMAXMean)
## 'data.frame':    1311 obs. of  5 variables:
##  $ Month: chr  "05" "04" "05" "06" ...
##  $ Year : chr  "1893" "1894" "1894" "1894" ...
##  $ TMAX : num  31.3 28.3 30.5 31.6 32.3 ...
##  $ YEAR : num  1893 1894 1894 1894 1894 ...
##  $ MONTH: num  5 4 5 6 7 8 9 2 3 4 ...
plot(MonthlyTMAXMean$TMAX, ty='l')

plot(TMAX~YEAR, data=MonthlyTMAXMean[MonthlyTMAXMean$Month=="12",], ty='l', xlim=c(1850, 2020)) 
May.lm <- lm(TMAX~YEAR, data=MonthlyTMAXMean[MonthlyTMAXMean$Month=="12",])
summary(May.lm)
